title: Familjen framför allt
description: Lena starts working as a bank head and she now earns more than Gustav. Her career inspires him to claim a promotion at the post office. Lina is delightful for soon being chosen as the centrist in school.

title: Rör inte min Volvo!
description: Even if the children are ashamed for not having a glamorous car as all of their neighbors, Gustav Svensson is a hopeless owner of Volvo. But he might change his mind when Sara buys a new, glamorous car which he gets to drive.

title: När gav du din fru en vävstol senast?
Brevbärare utan gränser
description: Gustav becomes firmly involved in the third world. Ment Well but much too complicated. He is simultaneously trying to help Max move to his new apartment. Even this gets very complicated.
